<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='651146' id='t-651146'>So this is important.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:04
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='653014' id='t-653014'>We have also some images of honey from Brooklyn.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='655121' id='t-655121'>Now, this was a mystery in the New York Times</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='657073' id='t-657073'>where the honey was very red, and the</span>
