<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='668818' id='t-668818'>So you can tailor your honey to taste however you want</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='672216' id='t-672216'>by planting bee-friendly flowers.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:25
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='674511' id='t-674511'>Paris has been a terrific model for urban beekeeping.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='677249' id='t-677249'>They've had hives on the rooftop of their opera house</span>
