<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='686203' id='t-686203'>Also in London, and in Europe across the board,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='689036' id='t-689036'>they're very advanced in their use of green rooftops</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='692288' id='t-692288'>and integrating beehives,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='694786' id='t-694786'>and I'll show you an ending note here.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
11:48
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='697967' id='t-697967'>I would like to encourage you to open your mind.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='700042' id='t-700042'>What can you do to save the bees or to help them</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='703203' id='t-703203'>or to think of sustainable cities in the future?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='706994' id='t-706994'>Well, really, just change your perspective.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='708964' id='t-708964'>Try to understand that bees are very important.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='710938' id='t-710938'>A bee isn't going to sting you if you see it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='713349' id='t-713349'>The bee dies. Honeybees die when they sting,</span>
